      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="footer" style="background-color:#cccccc; width:100%;height:auto; text-align:center;">
    <img style="padding:7px 0px;" src="images/roomnhouse-grey.png" width="121" />
    <div class="address" style="color: #888888; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; height: 15px; padding-bottom:5px;"> 201, J. B. Nagar, Off. Andheri Kurla Road, Andheri East, Mumbai-400059</div>
  </div>
</div>
